
Ranger Help for: archery
========================

SUMMARY:    
One of the identifying characteristics of a Ranger is his or her bow. Once
a Ranger gains enough potential as a Ranger, he or she may learn how to 
make various bows as well as ammo for the bows. They will also learn ways
to enhance arrows and bolts to make them more accurate or harder hitting.
Extremely proficient Rangers will learn special skills that increase the
lethality of their bows.

